{"arkId":"cl010103457","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010103457","modified ":"2025-09-02","title":"Bas-relief : l\u0027imp\u00e9ratrice Marie-Louise","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Bas-relief : l\u0027imp\u00e9ratrice Marie-Louise"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Premier Empire (1804-1814) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1810 - 1811","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 555 - Biennais, Vitrine table","room":"Salle 555, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1810,"endYear":1811,"imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Bonzanigo, Guiseppe Maria","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1745","place":"Asti","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1820","place":"Turin","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Sculpteur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3770905"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 364","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"bas-relief","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Portrait de trois-quarts face de l\u0027imp\u00e9ratrice Marie-Louise. La pr\u00e9sentation et le costume de cour n\u0027\u00e9voquent pas le portrait vaguement \u00e0 l\u0027antique alors tr\u00e8s diffus\u00e9. Les m\u00e9daillons repr\u00e9sentent trois dieux, Jupiter, Mars et Apollon, autant d\u0027avatars de son imp\u00e9rial \u00e9poux et trois all\u00e9gories des bienfaits qui doivent r\u00e9sulter de cette union : la Justice, la Paix et l\u0027Abondance. En dessous, en une sorte de pr\u00e9delle, de petits ivoires avec profils ou masques l\u00e9onins et de M\u00e9duse s\u0027int\u00e8grent maladroitement au dessin d\u0027ensemble. Ce n\u0027est pourtant pas une transformation post\u00e9rieure.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; MARIE LOUISE \/ ARCHIDUCHESS[E] D\u0027AUTRICHE \/ IMPERATRICE DE FRANCE \/ REINE D\u0027ITALIE","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"27","displayDimension":"27 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"17","displayDimension":"17 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"33,2","displayDimension":"33,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"23,8","displayDimension":"23,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9b\u00e8ne\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bois","placeOfCreation":"Italie (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Selon l\u0027inventaire de 1826, \u0022ces sculptures envoy\u00e9es par M. Bocenigo de Turin ont \u00e9t\u00e9 offertes \u00e0 Bonaparte [sic] et adress\u00e9es au Mus\u00e9e par le ministre de l\u0027int\u00e9rieur le 25 avril 1811 ; anciennement d\u00e9pos\u00e9 au Cabinet des Dessins de l\u0027UCAD ; arr\u00eat\u00e9 de fin de d\u00e9p\u00f4t le 27 juin 2005.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"period":[{"value":"Premier Empire (1804-1814)"}],"place":[{"value":"Italie"}],"objectType":[{"value":"bas-relief"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Malgou